      <p class="article-preamble">What is happening right now. This is the part of the site that updates while you read it.</p>
      <p>Paper 1 is on arXiv (or shortly will be). The research program continues. Paper 2 is in progress: applying the same complexity-sensitive framework to evaporating black holes, looking for an observer-disagreement crossover at the Page time. If it lands, it is a tier-one result. If it does not, it is a publishable null. Either way the work is open here.</p>
